title: Sample Custom Keywords in Katalon Studio
description: When creating a New Custom Keyword, you have   the options to generate sample custom keywords used for either Web,   Mobile or API testing. They provide a great example to learn how to   create custom keywords with proper coding convention in Katalon   Studio from scratch.
